Introduction

Doah, also known by her full name Kim Doah is a South Korean singer, rapper, and actress under FASCINO. She is a member of the girl group FANATICS and its sub-unit FLAVOR. She made her solo debut on May 23, 2023, with the digital single "Dream Walking". She is also known for participating in Mnet's reality survival shows Produce 48 & Girls Planet 999.
